data.description: JUST LIKE BRAND NEW!!! THIS GREAT FAMILY HOME COMPLETED IN 2022 FEATURES 5 BEDROOMS AND 2 1/2 BATHROOMS, WITH STAINED CONCRETE FLOORS THROUGH OUT, ABSOLUTELY NO CARPET AT ALL, SO EASY TO MAINTAIN.  THE LARGE GALLEY STYLED KITCHEN OFFERS MUCH STORAGE AND WORKSPACE WITH THE GRANITE COUNTERTOPS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, IT OPENS TO A LARGE DINING AREA THAT OVER LOOKS THE BACK YARD.  THE MASTER BEDROOM IS NICELY SIZED AND THE BATH HAS DUAL SINKS ON A LARGE VANITY AND SEPARATE BATH TUB AND SHOWER.  WONDERFUL HOME JUST OUTSIDE OF BELTON WITH FABULOUS BELTON SCHOOLS! COME SEE THIS ONE TODAY! SQUARE FOOTAGE SHALL BE VERIFIED BY BUYERS INDEPENDENT APPRAISAL.
